{"tid":1437604,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"難民之父張超雄議員，請入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-09T14:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T14:50:00.000Z","uid":167329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3176067a9e2c1d43499dc4a079688a1f9dc4d0","tid":1437604,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:42:35.000Z","msg":"聽咗個記者會都知你有睇開連登<br />\n想問番聲<br />\n1.手握香港兵權既你 會唔會叫埋南亞勇武加入<br />\n   為香港既自由法治而戰呢<br />\n2.另外可唔可以用你既愛去感動<br />\n   <span style=\"color: red;\">仲係流浮山食緊海鮮既南亞黑社會</span><br />\n   唔好再留係黑社會呢<br />\n   要知香港既福利又多 工作機會都多<br />\n   做黑社會又搵唔到咩野大錢 係咪先<br />\n<br />\n唔知你可唔可以回應一下呢"},{"pid":"cae46926fd692095c416686c464e78f5c30d8860","tid":1437604,"uid":167329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:42:56.000Z","msg":"推到比張議員見到"},{"pid":"60269c67cc6f7b975b749cac364b99a752671036","tid":1437604,"uid":167329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:43:06.000Z","msg":"推到比張議員見到"},{"pid":"47980d241a49bc60456e384e80b71db0fc7a46a2","tid":1437604,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"推到比張議員見到"},{"pid":"1befd9d9178aa9002a08f88f5b3687c6a185d21d","tid":1437604,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:43:34.000Z","msg":"推到比張議員見到"},{"pid":"b0694ee07c9d875eedb79c166742fdf2507ad889","tid":1437604,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:43:46.000Z","msg":"推到比張議員見到"},{"pid":"e9007382e40eaf416fda9c1e09189f46b174e5f5","tid":1437604,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"推到比張議員見到"},{"pid":"a48143102a494eb3e3c1ad7f19cbbcdbddd94223","tid":1437604,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:44:24.000Z","msg":"推到比張議員見到"},{"pid":"4d6bd3f4cb06d3ea7d973d918228cf411e2971f0","tid":1437604,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl